0get%20great%20pay%20while%20working%20closely%20with%20executives%20from%20large%20public%20companies.%20You%20get%20to%20brush%20up%20on%20your%20soft%20skills%20while%20picking%20up%20technical%20skills%20like%20financial%20modeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20lesson%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20time%20in%20investment%20banking%20was%20how%20to%20perform%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20tasks%20efficiently.%20It%20also%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%20when%20evaluating%20businesses.%20Working%20on%20deals%20honed%20my%20intellectual%20curiosity%20and%20sharpened%20my%20judgment%20when%20making%20investment%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ac3ef7e-287b-4520-b110-bd1330ef737a%5C%22%3EJoining%20OffDeal%20was%20a%20calculated%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20considered%20starting%20my%20career%20at%20a%20tech%20startup%20instead.%20What%20held%20me%20back%20was%20my%20own%20aversion%20to%20risk.%20I%20studied%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%2C%20where%20few%20people%20would%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20entrepreneurship.%20Investment%20banking%20was%20the%20safer%20and%20prestigious%20path%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20tangible%20skills%20to%20offer%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20or%20join%20a%20startup.%20Investment%20banking%20felt%20like%20a%20good%20way%20for%20me%20to%20build%20up%20my%20skills%20in%20the%20event%20that%20the%20right%20startup%20opportunity%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20working%20as%20an%20investment%20banker%20for%20three%20years%2C%20first%20at%20Piper%20Sandler%20and%20then%20at%20JPMorgan.%20Incidentally%2C%20both%20roles%20were%20based%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20which%20helped%20expose%20me%20to%20the%20startup%20culture%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%2021-year-olds%20start%20companies%20and%20raise%20millions%20of%20dollars%20was%20exhilarating.%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%20then%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20why%20can't%20I%20do%20that%20too%3F%20Why%20don't%20I%20join%20a%20startup%20and%20take%20a%20big%20risk%20myself%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20started%20speaking%20to%20founders%20and%20investors%20to%20map%20out%20the%20next%20steps%20of%20my%20career.%20One%20day%2C%20while%20scrolling%20through%20LinkedIn%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20post%20from%20Ori%20Eldarov%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20AI%20native%20investment%20bank%2C%20OffDeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20drawn%20to%20OffDeal's%20mission%20and%20its%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20software%20to%20address%20the%20exact%20pain%20points%20I%20faced%20as%20a%20junior%20banker%20at%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20focus%20on%20small%20businesses%20resonated%20with%20me%20at%20a%20personal%20level.%20My%20mom%20runs%20her%20own%20dental%20practice%20and%20is%20a%20small-business%20owner.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20most%20business%20brokers%20could%20not%20run%20a%20proper%20Wall%20Street-level%20process%20when%20handling%20transactions%20for%20small%20businesses.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20OffDeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afa9f7ff-5b20-40ad-bde4-05d4cb93c8d2%5C%22%3EOffDeal%20is%20like%20Jane%20Street%2C%20but%20for%20investment%20banking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20unique%20about%20OffDeal%20is%20how%20each%20deal%20we%20handle%20is%20handled%20by%20a%20two-person%20team%20comprising%20one%20banker%20and%20one%20engineer.%20So%20far%2C%20I%20have%20been%20working%20on%20deals%20with%20OffDeal's%20founding%20software%20engineer%2C%20Luis%20Ruiz%20Morel.%20Both%20of%20us%20get%20to%20take%20a%20cut%20out%20of%20the%20deals%20we%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20work%20a%20lot%20faster.%20At%20bulge%20bracket%20banks%20like%20JPMorgan%2C%20a%20company%20valuation%20could%20take%20weeks%20or%20even%20months%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20OffDeal%2C%20it%20can%20be%20completed%20in%20one%20to%20two%20days%20at%20most.%20I%20just%20need%20to%20work%20with%20Luis%20to%20conduct%20the%20valuation%20using%20our%20proprietary%20software.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20I%20had%20to%20painstakingly%20plug%20my%20numbers%20into%20an%20Excel%20spreadsheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20modeling.%20AI%20and%20technology%20have%20completely%20transformed%20my%20workflow%20as%20a%20banker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20I%20had%20to%20take%20notes%20manually%20when%20I%20sat%20in%20on%20Zoom%20calls.%20Now%2C%20AI%20can%20transcribe%20those%20calls%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20putting%20together%20pitchbooks%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20hours%20going%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20my%20managing%20director%20and%20clients%20to%20polish%20them.%20Instead%2C%20our%20AI%20agent%20makes%20those%20revisions%20automatically%2C%20which%20saves%20us%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upside%20to%20all%20this%20is%20that%20our%20bankers%20can%20do%20more%20deals%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20spend%20less%20time%20on%20grunt%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20at%20JPMorgan%2C%20I%20usually%20worked%20on%20two%20to%20three%20live%20deals%20at%20once.%20Here%20at%20OffDeal%2C%20I%20can%20work%20on%2010%20to%2011%20deals%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20also%20get%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20out%20on%20the%20road%20meeting%20with%20prospective%20buyers%20and%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f460f09a-84d7-47c6-b38b-91f8d09517e5%5C%22%3ENow's%20the%20best%20time%20to%20join%20an%20AI%20startup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20starting%20your%20career%2C%20you%20can't%20go%20wrong%20with%20a%20job%20in%20traditional%20investment%20banking.%20It's%20still%20a%20great%20industry%20to%20go%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20think%20it%20has%20become%20less%20risky%20to%20join%20an%20AI%20company%20like%20OffDeal.%20It%20may%20have%20been%20a%20bigger%20risk%20before%2C%20but%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20AI%20will%20have%20a%20huge%20