.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-cross-country-road-trip-pit-stops-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecultural%20pit%20stops%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20hadn't%20considered.%20Hammamet%20was%20stripped%20back%20to%20a%20cultural%20visit%20to%20the%20Kasbah%20and%20an%20early%20dinner%20overlooking%20the%20water.%20Less%20cinematic%2C%20more%20logical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0d5c2b5-6e52-4707-9b23-255ebe4ff5cf%5C%22%3EReality%20quickly%20tested%20both%20AI%20itineraries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we%20then%20needed%20to%20build%20our%20own%20itinerary%2C%20taking%20activities%20recommended%20by%20both%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20ambitious%20Tozeur%20day%20nearly%20flattened%20us.%20The%20long%20drive%20was%20far%20from%20the%20breezy%20jaunt%20it%20implied%2C%20and%20when%20we%20finally%20got%20close%2C%20a%20sandstorm%20had%20blocked%20the%20highway.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Star%20Wars%26quot%3B%20sets%20were%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20proof%20that%20no%20itinerary%20can%20control%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20other%20parts%20of%20ChatGPT's%20plan%20delivered%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Sidi%20Bou%20Sa%C3%AFd%2C%20where%20whitewashed%20walls%20and%20cobalt-blue%20shutters%20glowed%20in%20the%20sun%20as%20we%20sipped%20mint%20tea%20above%20the%20sea.%20It%20felt%20like%20stepping%20into%20a%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-thing-to-do-while-traveling-food-tour-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Tunis%20was%20a%20big%20highlight.%20We%20enjoyed%20sesame-coated%20pastries%20as%20we%20drifted%20through%20narrow%20streets%2C%20pointing%20toward%20stalls%20and%20corners%20we%20would%20never%20have%20found%20on%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaude%20also%20surprised%20us%20with%20two%20inspired%20detours%3A%20the%20Great%20Mosque%20of%20Kairouan%20and%20El%20Jem%20amphitheater.%20Both%20were%20extraordinary%20stops%2C%20layered%20with%20history%20and%