al-security-job-training-lower-income-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20on%20social%20security%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20seen%20too%20many%20teachers%20where%20they're%20holding%20on%20until%20they%20turn%2065%2C%20and%20then%20they're%20going%20to%20retire%20and%20go%20on%20social%20security%2C%20and%20six%20months%20later%20they're%20six%20feet%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-grow-savings-one-million-using-fire-methods-investing-saving-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFIRE%20method%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20spent%20probably%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20last%2020%20years%20investing%20each%20time%20I%20got%20a%20pay%20raise.%20It%20worked%20out%20favorably%20for%20me%20over%20the%20last%2020%20or%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202013%2C%20I%20noticed%20an%20influx%20of%20migrant%20students%20coming%20into%20my%20classroom%20from%20Guatemala%2C%20Honduras%2C%20or%20El%20Salvador%2C%20and%20I%20got%20to%20know%20some%20of%20these%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20skyscraper%20being%20built%20in%20Guatemala%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e809fe5dbc4fd10daa8f88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20skyscraper%20being%20built%20in%20Guatemala%20City.%3Cp%3ERon%20Podmore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20led%20to%20believe%20that%20Guatemala%20is%20this%20country%20with%20endemic%20poverty%2C%20crime%2C%20corruption%2C%20cartels%20%E2%80%94%20who%20on%20earth%20would%20want%20to%20go%20down%20there%3F%20And%20these%20kids%20really%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20rethink%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20encouraged%20me%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-trip-to-central-america-better-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20to%20Guatemala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%202013%20or%202014%2C%20I%20took%20my%20first%20trip%20down%20there.%20Then%20I%20ended%20up%20going%20down%20there%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232ccf289-19d5-40dd-b1c6-94088d1bb7c3%5C%22%3EI%20paid%20off%20my%20Guatemala%20condo%20in%20under%2010%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20purchased%20a%20small%20condominium%20in%20the%20working-class%20area%20of%20Guatemala%20City%2C%20knowing%20that%20if%20I%20needed%20to%2C%20I%20could%20migrate%20out%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20be%20able%20to%20live%20down%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20had%20already%20purchased%20the%20property%20as%20an%20investment%20before%20I%20retired%2C%20and%20then%20I%20was%20able%20to%20make%20payments%20on%20it.%20My%20goal%20was%20to%20have%20it%20all%20paid%20off%20by%20the%20time%20I%20retired.%20And%20sure%20enough%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20it%20all%20off%2C%20so%20I%20have%20no%20mortgage%20on%20that%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20making%20payments%20on%20it%20every%20month%2C%20and%20then%20I%20also%20expedited%20that%20by%20making%20extra%20payments%20on%20the%20principal%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20it%20off%20within%20eight%20years.%20In%20order%20to%20do%20that%2C%20I%20took%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flandlord-couple-heloc-rental-real-estate-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHELOC%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20value%20of%20the%20house%20that%20I%20have%20in%20Federal%20Way%2C%20which%20is%20a%20suburb%20just%20south%20of%20Seattle.%20When%20you%20purchase%20property%2C%20in%20most%20places%20around%20the%20world%2C%20it's%20all%20cash.%20You%20cannot%20go%20to%20the%20bank%20of%20that%20country%20and%20ask%20for%20a%20loan.%20You%20have%20to%20take%20care%20of%20your%20financing%20with%20whatever%20bank%20you%20have%20in%20the%20United%20States%20or%20your%20home%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20that%20I%20purchased%20down%20there%20is%20a%20two-bedroom%2C%20one-bath%20with%20underground%20parking%2C%20concierge%20services%2C%20security%2C%20et%20cetera%2C%20and%20that%20was%20for%20about%20%24125%2C000.%20The%20mortgage%20was%20for%2010%20years%2C%20just%20under%20%241%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22726%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20skyline%20in%20Guatemala.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e809a05dbc4fd10daa8f6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20Podmore's%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3ERon%20Podmore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20renting%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20vacant%20for%20years.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20for%20me%20to%20begin%20furnishing%2C%20purchasing%20things%20like%20the%20couches%2C%20and%20the%20chairs%2C%20and%20the%20dining%20room%20tables%2C%20and%20the%20beds%2C%20and%20stuff%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20do%20that%20little%20by%20little%20over%20the%20eight%20years.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Washington%20State%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20factor%20in%20airplane%20tickets%20to%20get%20down%20there%2C%20and%20how%20much%20money%20you're%20going%20to%20spend%20on%20not%20only%20purchasing%20these%20items%2C%20but%20also%20having%20them%20delivered%20and%20being%20there%20and%20so%20forth.%20It%20took%20me%20about%20two%20or%20three%20years%20to%20build%20it%20all%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20being%20down%20there%20full-time%20in%20August%202024.%20I'm%20in%20the%20process%20of%20securing%20a%20temporary%20and%20a%20permanent%20residency%20card.%20That's%20about%20a%20three-%20to%20five-year%20long%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20be%20getting%20a%20visa%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20live%20in%20Guatemala%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20greater%20than%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20as%20it%20is%2C%20I'm%20only%20allowed%20to%20stay%20in%20Guatemala%20up%20to%20six%20months%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f883d7a5-e1fe-4790-858a-69c0a6a94717%5C%22%3EThe%20healthcare%20in%20Guatemala%20is%20significantly%20less%20expensive%20than%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20private%20health%20insurance%20plan%20in%20Guatemala%20that%20runs%20me%20about%20%24315%20a%20month%3B%20no%20deductibles%20and%20no%20copay.%20That's%20a%20private%20hospital%20that%20also%20covers%20medicines%2C%20X-rays%2C%20MRIs%2C%20and%20hospital%20stays%2C%20and%20you%20do%20not%20get%20a%20bill%20at%20the%20end%20of%20any%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20is%20such%20a%20contrast%20for%20superior%20services%3A%20they%20have%20better%20bedside%20manners%20in%20Central%20America.%20You're%20not%20surrounded%20by%20a%20certified%20nursing%20assistant%20or%20an%20intake%20specialist%20or%20a%20finance%20and%20operations%20person%20determining%20how%20are%20you%20going%20to%20make%20these%20payments%20and%20everything.%20You%20go%20into%20an%20office%2C%20the%20reception%20is%20right%20there%2C%20and%20the%20second%20person%20you%20see%20is%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221809%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20overlooking%20Guatemala%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e809cf1c1f80efbec54c2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221382%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPodmore%20overlooking%20Guatemala%20City.%3Cp%3ERon%20Podmore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGlasses%2C%20optometry%2C%20and%20dental%20I%20am%20not%20insured%20on.%20When%20I'm%20down%20there%20I%20get%20my%20teeth%20cleaned%20every%20six%20months%2C%20just%20like%20I%20do%20up%20here%2C%20and%20my%20teeth%20cleaning%20on%20average%20is%20about%20%2465%20per%20visit.%20To%20contrast%20that%2C%20when%20I%20was%20going%20to%20get%20my%20teeth%20cleaned%20at%20my%20local%20dentist%20up%20here%20in%20Washington%2C%20that%20would%20be%20close%20to%20%24800%20or%20%24900.%20What%20the%20insurance%20carrier%20for%20dental%20is%20not%20covering%20of%20that%20is%20forced%20onto%20me.%20So%20each%20time%20I%20went%20to%20get%20my%20teeth%20cleaned%20in%20the%20States%2C%20it%20was%20slightly%20over%20%24200%20for%20my%20portion%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20about%20the%20concept%20of%20snowbirds%2C%20at%20least%20out%20here%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%20we%20have%20a%20huge%20influx%20of%20people%20in%20their%20fifties%20who%20decide%20to%20retire%20early%20and%20they%20immediately%20relocate%20to%20Southern%20California%2C%20Southern%20Arizona%2C%20Southern%20New%20Mexico%2C%20in%20border%20towns%20all%20along%20the%20Texas%20border%2C%20so%20they%20can%20have%20immediate%20access%20%E2%80%94%20to%20drive%20to%20the%20border%20or%20walk%20across%20the%20border%20%E2%80%94%20to%20purchase%20their%20prescriptions%2C%20get%20their%20teeth%20done%2C%20get%20their%20X-rays%20done%2C%20or%20go%20into%20the%20local%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20an%20emergency%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20run%20over%20to%20that%20border%20before%20they%20dial%20911%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20just%20taken%20that%20concept%20one%20extra%20country%20over%2C%20which%20is%20the%20next%20country%20after%20Mexico%2C%20and%20that's%20Guatemala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiring-early-guatemala-cheaper-healthcare-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760265541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e951ae5dbc4fd10daaa665%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiring-early-guatemala-cheaper-healthcare-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ron%20Podmore%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Central%20America.%20He%20decided%20to%20retire%20in%20Guatemala%20at%2056%2