%20agency%20based%20in%20London%2C%20where%20he%20now%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222217%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grant%20Miller%20in%20London%20in%20May%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689b4572a17a8c5b4052b270%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221663%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrant%20Miller%20in%20London%20in%20May%202025.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Grant%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20signing%20up%20in%20September%202024%2C%20he%20said%20he%20has%20paid%20about%20%C2%A320%2C000%2C%20or%20about%20%2426%2C000%2C%20and%20been%20introduced%20to%2016%20women%20through%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20a%20very%20'open'%20approach%20as%20I%20was%20available%20and%20enjoyed%20meeting%20new%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20dates%20turned%20into%20short%20relationships%20or%20friendships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20connection%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20long-term%20potential%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%26quot%3Bour%20schedules%20and%20lifestyles%20need%20some%20alignment%2C%20which%20has%20been%20challenging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he's%20said%20it's%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20multiply%20the%20time%20you'd%20spend%20dating%20by%20your%20hourly%20rate%2C%20the%20fees%20suddenly%20become%20not%20so%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20value%20my%20time%2C%20and%20I'm%20serious%20about%20finding%20the%20right%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f59c7d2-3524-40bc-91a3-9633b026a60a%5C%22%3EThe%20data%20behind%20the%20dating%20shift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20clients%20prefer%20to%20stay%20anonymous%2C%20four%20matchmaking%20firms%20told%20BI%20they're%20seeing%20a%20clear%20increase%20in%20demand%20from%20HNW%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelective%20Search%2C%20a%20US-based%20firm%2C%20said%20it's%20seen%20a%2035%25%20increase%20in%20clients%20since%202019%20and%20a%2065%