-id%3D%5C%2296fec584-5432-4235-8940-508f5b6dccf8%5C%22%3EWho%20these%20men%20are%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20they're%20doing%20this%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Miller%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20matchmaking%20isn't%20just%20about%20convenience%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20increasing%20his%20chances%20of%20finding%20someone%20exceptional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20start%20doing%20percentages%20of%20percentages%20of%20percentages.%20And%20you're%20down%20to%20like%20one%20in%20a%20hundred%20thousand%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20meet%20a%20hundred%20women%20on%20my%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20matters%20most%20to%20Miller%20is%20ambition%20and%20emotional%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinancial%20success%20doesn't%20always%20translate%20to%20romantic%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20kind%20of%20narrows%20the%20dating%20pool%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20someone%20who's%20not%20intimidated%20or%20overly%20motivated%20by%20wealth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22893%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grant%20Miller%20in%20Banff%2C%20Alberta%2C%20in%20October%202021.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689b45b2cfc04e97619b3ddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221471%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrant%20Miller%20in%20Banff%2C%20Alberta%2C%20in%20October%202021.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Grant%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMatchmaking%20helps%20with%20that%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they're%20very%20good%20at%20sniffing%20out%20%E2%80%94%20for%20lack%20of%20a%20better%20word%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20kind%20of%20'gold%20digger.'%20I'm%20looking%20for%20someone%20who's%20additive%20to%20my%20life.%20And%20who's%20bringing%20their%20own%20value%20to%20the%20equation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266e9c3bd-967d-4bd9-80e5-0b599413bb84%5C%22%3EHow%20matchmaking%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20