how%20people%20outsource%20what%20used%20to%20be%20a%20very%20personal%2C%20familial%2C%20and%20institutionally-based%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-make-5000-month-sudshare-laundry-service-app-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoutsource%20their%20laundry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20outsource%20their%20food%20delivery%2C%20they%20outsource%2C%20you%20know%2C%20major%20parts%20of%20their%20fitness%20to%20a%20coach%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20not%20outsource%20one%20other%20element%20of%20their%20life%2C%20which%20is%20highly%20salient%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepper%20Schwartz%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20sociology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington%20and%20coauthor%20of%20%26quot%3BRelationship%20Rx%3A%20Prescriptions%20for%20Lasting%20Love%20and%20Deeper%20Connection%2C%26quot%3B%20concurred%20%E2%80%94%20but%20added%20that%20many%20wealthy%20men%20believe%20price%20equals%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20money%20will%20buy%20you%20a%20better%20product%2C%20a%20better%20treat%2C%20a%20better%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20that%20is%20true%20or%20not%2C%20that's%20the%20theory%20that%20many%20of%20them%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20warned%20the%20matchmaker%20pool%20may%20be%20smaller%20than%20clients%20realize%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20usually%20believe%20there's%20more%20denominator%20available%20than%20is%20actually%20there%2C%20and%20they%20haven't%20done%20the%20homework%20to%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20pressure%20to%20partner%20up%20later%20in%20life%20is%20real%20%E2%80%94%20and%20high-end%20matchmaking%20offers%20the%20illusion%20of%20control%20in%20what%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20high-stakes%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20hope%20that%20something%20will%20just%20happen%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%